<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sunshine-n">sunshine <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sʌnʃaɪn/    美 /'sʌnʃaɪn/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>阳光；晴天；欢乐：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>After rain comes sunshine. 
雨过天晴。/苦尽甘来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her smile brought a <strong>ray of sunshine</strong> into the room.
她的微笑给这个房间带来了一丝欢乐。</p></div></div>